text.tspan: Onshore wind cost vs. wind energy generation
Global weighted average levelized cost of electricity (LCOE) from onshore wind versus the annual wind electricity
consumption is measured in 2016 USD per kilowatt-hour (kWh). Wind energy generation is measured in kWh.
Source: IRENA Cost Database (2018), BP Statistical Review of Global Energy
